name: v3.0.1
body:
This release merely includes a fix for a bug introduced in v3.0.1.

See the changelog [here](http://todoman.readthedocs.io/en/v3.0.0/changelog.html) for details.

Oops! This release had a packaging error. Please don't use it!

Also, we skipped the changelog for it. See the following release's changelog [here](http://todoman.readthedocs.io/en/v2.0.2/changelog.html) for details.
